## Project Overview :page_facing_up:

If this application is in response to an RFP, please indicate this on the first line of this section.

If this is an application for a follow-up grant (the continuation of an earlier, successful W3F grant), please provide name and/or pull request of said grant on the first line of this section.

### Overview

Please provide the following:

- A Play-To-Earn Metaverse Expereience.
- Solospace is a project in the works being built on Bit.Country Polkadot and Kusama Infrastructure, we plan on providing a unique experience of the Metaverse with vrious atributes, such as collaborations with well known influencers to perform in Solospace.io as well as inprire and provide a hub for fellow developers to earn and play in our community as it growns with Bit.Country and the Metaverse.Network 
- We are being buit in partnership with the team of Ray Lu and Bit.Country on the Polkadot and Kusama Infrastructure 
- Our team is truly passionate about creating a Metaverse experience for our users that will inspire the next generation to not only benefit economically thru our play-to-earn incentives, but we are also excited to provide a platform for users to experience and socialize as AR technology comes along, we feel like we can utilize our relashipships with unluencers to join our mission of the Metaverse and further grow our community together.

