### Ecosystem Fit

Help us locate your project in the Polkadot/Substrate/Kusama landscape and what problems it tries to solve by answering each of these questions:

- Our project will fit as a community experience Metaverse within the Bit.Country ecosystem and be a hub where users can access Perfomances (we are in discussions with Calvin Harris and Imagine Dragons, among others that we will disclose upon completion of confidentially. 
- Target Audience will be anyone, our own user base, dapp's userbase, and Bit.Country userbase. 
- What need(s) does your project meet?
- Are there any other projects similar to yours in the Substrate / Polkadot / Kusama ecosystem?
  - If so, how is your project different?
  - If not, are there similar projects in related ecosystems?

